text.div: • Include codes from http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActRelationshipCheckpoint where concept is-a E

name: ActRelationshipCheckpointEnd
title: ActRelationshipCheckpointEnd
description: Condition is tested at the end of a repeated service execution. The service is repeated only if the condition is true (DO service WHILE condition).
